    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund climate-ready updates to homes, businesses and infrastructure",
        "additional_details": "The UK Government has failed to meaningfully update public infrastructure so that our public transport and businesses can continue to operate in increasingly dramatic climate conditions. These last few years we have seen all-time highs in temperatures and extreme flooding.\r\n \r\nWe ask that the Government start work to make Britain climate-ready, including by funding updates to British homes.",
        "background": "The UK Government must take meaningful action to update public infrastructure and support updates to British homes and businesses in readiness for increasingly dramatic climate conditions.",
